<h3>Google Search Console Is the Only Definitive Source</h3>
<p><a href="/blog/google-search-console-guide/">Google Search Console</a> tells you exactly two things no other tool can:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Manual Actions</strong>. If Google has penalized your site for unnatural links, it appears here. This is the only confirmed "toxic link" signal.</li>
<li><strong>Links Report</strong>. Shows every link Google has found pointing to your site. Use this as your ground truth for link data.</li>
</ol>
<p>If you have no manual action in Search Console, the urgency of toxic link cleanup drops significantly.</p>
<h3>How to Run a Toxic Link Audit</h3>
<ol>
<li>Export your full backlink profile from Search Console and your preferred SEO tool</li>
