<li>Sort by <a href="/glossary/referring-domain/">referring domain</a> to identify patterns</li>
<li>Flag links matching the 10 red flags from Chapter 3</li>
<li>Verify each flagged link manually before acting</li>
</ol>
<p>Do NOT rely solely on a tool's toxicity score. Manual verification catches false positives that automated detection misses.</p>
